name: Flytime for Froggo
description:
This game was made for: "Mini Jam 106: Frogs^2".

https://itch.io/jam/mini-jam-106-frogs

This game was made in 3 days.

Flytime for Froggo is a game about feasting on flies, lilypads, and a good 'ole time at the pond.

The limitation was "Limited Time"

*Note: WASD or arrow keys to move*
